{"tid":261312,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"2016-17 LIHKG香港冠軍女神聯賽升班附決賽-張曦雯vs岑麗香","createTime":"2017-05-28T10:59:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-28T17:27:45.000Z","uid":92376,"like":56,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e1f7740235dfbbbb2113bf1531a4551fe16ea593","tid":261312,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T10:59:59.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">LIHKG香港冠軍女神聯賽升班附加賽決賽</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-5-28 *括號內數字為聯賽最終排名</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/y62ciOO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fy62ciOO.png&h=e05c5d4c&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/krRMKZI.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FkrRMKZI.png&h=8d9c4b3d&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(3)張曦雯vs岑麗香(5)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">升班附加賽決賽賽時為六小時，會員可於本帖發起後六小時內於以正負評方式(前者正評;後者負評)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的正負評投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">附加賽不設額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"84a071b3c026c5154ee6c5ef7ea49c43965dd2f7","tid":261312,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T11:00:11.000Z","msg":"今場勝出女神將會獲得來季即17-18季度超級女神聯賽最後一個升班名額,請大家踴躍支持吧"},{"pid":"c0b695598386df7d79fe083d4e91852e7597c561","tid":261312,"uid":90,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T11:00:30.000Z","msg":"兩件都唔掂"},{"pid":"6d3cac4d7d1f808354f70842b880b03751a083c7","tid":261312,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T11:00:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩件都唔掂</blockquote><br />\n你游B最掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.p